vedo che citi un flusso che vada direttamente da libreoffice ad RST, questa sarebbe un'alternativa a pandoc se non mi sbaglio?

the same handling is given to nested links now, so for example *italics [link]() italics* is turned into *italics* [link]() *italics*, which is not what is proposed in 4339 but it keeps more information than the behaviour i proposed earlier

